ontrol of ultra-high voltage half-wavelength and DC hybrid system based on steady state characteristics. Automation of Electric Power Systems, 41(22)： 26-32</p><p name=\"ref16\" style=\"font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.8em; margin: 0.5em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">[16] Wang G (2011) Exploration research on some key issues of the UHV half-wavelength transmission technology. Dissertation,Shandong University</p><p name=\"ref17\" style=\"font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.8em; margin: 0.5em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">[17] Wang A, Ren D, Tang Y et al (2017) Study on power transmission capability of the UHV half-wavelength transmission system. Power System Technology, 41(10)： 3168-3173</p><p name=\"ref18\" style=\"font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.8em; margin: 0.5em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">[18] Zang L, Zou L, Lv X et al (2012) Power frequency temporary overvoltage on half-wavelength AC transmission lines. High Voltage Engineering, 38(10)： 2728-2734</p><p name=\"ref19\" style=\"font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.8em; margin: 0.5em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">[19] Zhou J, Ma J, Xu H et al (2011) Steady state and transient operational characteristics of UHV half-wavelength AC transmission system. Power System Technology, 35(9)： 28-32</p><p name=\"ref20\" style=\"font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.8em; margin: 0.5em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">[20] Han B, Lin J, Ban L et al (2011) Analysis on electromagnetic transient characteristics of UHV half-wavelength AC transmission system. Power System Technology, 35(9)： 22-27</p><p name=\"ref21\" style=\"font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.8em; margin: 0.5em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">[21] Lou Y, Zhou P, Xiu M et al (2012) Electromagnetic transient simulation of UHV half-wavelength AC transmission line. High Voltage Engineering, 38(6)： 1459-1465</p><p name=\"ref22\" style=\"font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.8em; margin: 0.5em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;\">[2